data.description: Beautifully updated home. Everything about this floor plan is wonderful. Home has tons of storage and every room has at least one walk in closet, huge pantry with built-in desk area. Upstairs suite is MASSIVE and has it's own bath. Downstairs has a powder bath, and jack & jill bath has built in dressers too! Front walk is tiles all the way to the front door, sun porch is amazing, and there are extra tall ceilings throughout.
